es.stuker.buker.ipv6multidest.webserver

Class Multiplexer

  • java.lang.Object
    • es.stuker.buker.ipv6multidest.webserver.Multiplexer

  • class Multiplexer
extends java.lang.Object
    Webserver answer multiplexer simulator. Contains output list and slot parameter. Receives request objects and date updates periodically. Tries to match requests in an output list then pops them when new date exceeds timeout.
    Author:
    Jorge D'iez de la Fuente
